                    <div class="article-1__hero">
                    <div class="article-1__hero-quote">THREE OWLS WHO CHANGED DIRECTION TOWARD A BRIGHTER FUTURE</div>
                    <div class="article-1__hero-byline">by: <span>Laila Samphilipo</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="article-1__hero-text">
                    <p><strong>Across the workforce and in educational institutions, refinement is seemingly inevitable as people encounter new experiences that challenge their current systems and beliefs.</strong><p>
                        <p>Naturally, many students, faculty and alumni at the Fox School have refined their approach to their professional and educational careers. Here are three examples of Owls who've made adjustments to alter the trajectory of their future.</p>
</div>
                    </div>

            </div>
        </div><!-- article-1__container -->
